actions.name: Send Message

actions.message:
**DBM Helper Role:**
That role is for users who know much about DBM
because it can be mentioned for help reasons.
`!helper`

**Suggestions:**
You can suggest stuff for the bot/server/DBM. Please write exactly what you want!
`!suggest [text]`

**Warnings:**
Moderators can warn you. If you reached a specific amount of warning points, you'll get kicked/banned.
`!warnings`

**Info commands:**
You can use premade messages to answer to often asked questions
using our "info" command.
 
Type **!info [infoname]** to get such a message.
Infonames:
`beta`, `mods`, `rawdata`, `vps`, `tutorials`, `srd`, `verify`, `embed`, `./nodemodules`, `cmd`, `mac`, `forum`, `moduleerror`, `enduserdata`, `music`, `helper`, `scripts`, `suggestions`, `one-channel`, `servers`, `token`, `achievements`, `support-website`, `expert`, `supporter`, `help`

**My data?**
If you want to check what we saved from you please use this command:
`!mydata`
